    "We also conduct ablation studies to understand the contribution of each component in our method.",
    "Specifically, we aim to answer the following research questions: (a) How does RIFL perform on challenging instruction-following benchmarks?",
    "(b) How effective is the finetuned rubric verifier in providing reliable feedback for training compared to the vanilla LLM judge prompted with rubrics?",
    "(c) What is the impact of different reward designs on the performance of RIFL?",
    "(d) Does the reward shaping technique help mitigate reward hacking issues in RIFL?"
  ],
